OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be mainly cloudy with a few
OL,7,Foutbreaks of rain in north and west,
OL,8,Fbut brighter along east coast. Then
OL,9,Fthe rest of the night will be cloudy
OL,10,Fwith occasional rain in the west,
OL,11,Fmainly dry in east.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FMostly cloudy, with a little
OL,14,Frain at times, mainly across northern
OL,15,FTayside and across the Trossachs.
OL,16,FMostly dry with brighter spells in the
OL,17,Feastern Central Belt, where quite warm.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
