OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Wednesday to Friday:FA
OL,6,Fmainly dry few days with variable
OL,7,Famounts of cloud and some spells of
OL,8,Fsunshine. Perhaps some heavy showers
OL,9,Flate Friday. Very warm or hot.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
